# Partrunner Brand Identity

## Colors (STRICT — only these 3 for brand elements)

- `#FDD238` — Partrunner Yellow (headlines, accents, vests)
- `#000000` — Black (logo backgrounds, secondary text)
- `#FFFFFF` — White (contrast)
- Scene colors can be natural — restriction applies to typography, logo, brand overlays

## Editorial style

- Genre: "Hiperrealismo cinematográfico + surrealismo logístico"
- Surreal/absurd scenes where Partrunner logistics solves the impossible
- Smart Mexican humor — irreverent but never vulgar
- Every image MUST have: branded vehicle, worker with vest, surreal element, cinematic lighting

## Logo rules

- Logo URLs are real Supabase URLs — don't replace them
- Logo must always be present in generated concepts (on vehicle or worker vest)
- AI image models CANNOT render actual logos — use as metadata for post-processing

## Text in images

- AI models CANNOT reliably render text
- `prompt_compiled` should include "leave clean negative space for text overlay"
- Headlines are generated as METADATA, not as image generation instructions
